M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single]
M109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer]
PRINT_START EXTRUDER=[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] BED=[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single]
; You can use following code instead if your PRINT_START macro support Chamber and print area bedmesh
; PRINT_START EXTRUDER=[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] BED=[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single] Chamber=[chamber_temperature] PRINT_MIN={first_layer_print_min[0]},{first_layer_print_min[1]} PRINT_MAX={first_layer_print_max[0]},{first_layer_print_max[1]}
variants.endGcode: PRINT_END

variants.name: Anycubic 4Max Pro 2 0.4 nozzle
variants.startGcode:
G21 ; metric values
G90 ; absolute positioning
M82 ; set extruder to absolute mode
M140 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ; set bed temp
G28 X0 Y0 ; home X and Y
G28 Z0 ; home Z
G1 Z30 F{machine_max_speed_z[0]*60} ; move Z a bit down to not blow on the bed edge while heating
G1 X10 F3900 ; let some space on x to prevent the filament cooling exhaust from beeing blocked by the servo motor
M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single] ; wait for bed temp
M104 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ; set extruder temp
M106 S80 ; turn on fan to prevent air nozzle melt while heating up
M109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ; wait for extruder temp
M107 ; start with the fan off
G28 X0 ; goto X home again
G92 E0 ; zero the extruded length
G1 Z0.2 F360 ; move plattform upwards
; extrude material next to the plattform (comment or remove following lines to disable)
G1 F180 E20 ; extrude some material next to the plattform
G92 E0 ; zero the extruded length
G1 E-[retraction_length] F{retraction_speed[0]*60} ; do a filament retract
G92 E0 ; zero the extruded length again
G1 X5 F3900 ; move sideways to get rid of that string
G1 E[retraction_length] F{retraction_speed[0]*60} ; do a filament deretract with retract parameters
G92 E0 ; zero the extruded length again
; draw intro line (comment or remove following lines to disable)
G1 X30 E5 F700 ; draw intro line
G92 E0 ; zero the extruded length
G1 E-[retraction_length] F{retraction_speed[0]*60} ; do a filament retract
G1 X40 Z2.0 ; move away from the introline
G92 E0 ; zero the extruded length again
G1 E[retraction_length] F{retraction_speed[0]*60} ; do a filament deretract with retract parameters
; end of intro line code
M117 Printing...
G5
variants.endGcode:
M104 S0 ; turn off extruder heating
M140 S0 ; turn off bed heating
M107 ; turn off fans
G91 ; relative positioning
G0 Z+0.5 ; move Z up a tiny bit
G90 ; absolute positioning
G0 X135 Y105 F{machine_max_speed_x[0]*60} ; move extruder to center position
G0 Z190.5 F{machine_max_speed_z[0]*60} ; lower the plattform to Z min
M84 ; steppers off
G90 ; absolute positioning

variants.name: Anycubic Chiron 0.4 nozzle
variants.startGcode:
M104 S140;start the nozzle preheat and don't wait
G21;metric values
G90;absolute positioning
M82;set extruder to absolute mode
M107       ;start with the fan off
G28;home all
M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single]; set wait for bed temp
M109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ; wait for extruder temp
G1 Z15.0 F3600 ;move the platform down 15mm
G92 E0;zero the extruded length
G1 F200 E40;extrude 40mm of feed stock
G92 E0;zero the extruded length again
G1 F3600
variants.endGcode:
M104 S0;extruder heater off
M140 S0  ;heated bed heater off (if you have it)
G91;relative positioning
G1 E-4 F300;retract the filament a bit before lifting the nozzle, to release some of the pressure
G1 Z+10 F3600 ;move Z up a bit
G90;absolute positioning
G1 X-10 F3000; get the head off the bed
G1 F3000 Y400;kick the bed out
M84;steppers off

variants.name: Anycubic Kobra 0.4 nozzle
variants.startGcode:
G90 ; use absolute coordinates
M83 ; extruder relative mode
M204 P[machine_max_acceleration_extruding] R[machine_max_acceleration_retracting] T[machine_max_acceleration_travel]
M104 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ; set extruder temp
M140 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single] ; set bed temp
G28 ; home all
G1 Y1.0 Z0.3 F{travel_speed*60} ; move print head up
M190 S[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single] ; wait for bed temp
M109 S[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] ; wait for extruder temp
G92 E0.0
; initial load
G1 X205.0 E19 F1000
G1 Y1.6
G1 X5.0 E19 F1000
G92 E0.0
; intro line
G1 Y2.0 Z0.2 F1000
G1 X65.0 E9.0 F1000
G1 X105.0 E12.5 F1000
G92 E0.0
variants.endGcode:
G1 E-1.0 F2100 ; retract
G92 E0.0
G1 X0{if max_layer_z < printable_height} Z{z_offset+min(max_layer_z+30, printable_height)}{endif} E-34.0 F{travel_speed*60} ; move print head up & retract filament
G4 ; wait
M104 S0 ; turn off temperature
M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M107 ; turn off fan
G1 X0 Y105 F{travel_speed*60} ; park print head
M84 ; disable motors

variants.name: Anycubic Kobra 2 0.4 nozzle
variants.startGcode:
G90 ;Use absolute coordinates
M83 ;Extruder relative mode
M104 S[first_layer_temperature] ;Set extruder temp
M140 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ;Set bed temp
M190 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ;Wait for bed temp
M109 S[first_layer_temperature] ;Wait for extruder temp
G28 ;Move X/Y/Z to min endstops
G1 Z0.28 ;Lift nozzle a bit
G92 E0 ;Specify current extruder position as zero
G1 Y3 F1800 ;Move Y to purge point
G1 X60 E25 F500 ;Extrude 25mm of filament in a 5cm line
G92 E0 ;Zero the extruded length again
G1 E-2 F500 ;Retract a little
G1 X70 F4000 ;Quickly wipe away from the filament line
M117
variants.endGcode:
M104 S0 ;Extruder off
M140 S0 ;Heatbed off
M107 ;Fan off
G91 ;Relative positioning
G1 E-5 F3000 ;Retract filament
G1 Z+0.3 F3000 ;Lift print head
G28 X0 F3000 ;Home X axis
M84 ;Disable stepper motors

defaultMaterials: Anycubic PLA SE @Anycubic Kobra 2 Plus 0.4 nozzle
Anycubic PLA High Speed @Anycubic Kobra 2 Plus 0.4 nozzle

Anycubic PLA Slik @Anycubic Kobra 2 Plus 0.4 nozzle

variants.name: Anycubic Kobra 2 Plus 0.4 nozzle
variants.startGcode:
G90 ; use absolute coordinates
M83 ; extruder relative mode
M140 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ; set bed temp
M190 S[first_layer_bed_temperature] ; wait for bed temp
M104 S[first_layer_temperature] ; set extruder temp
M109 S[first_layer_temperature] ; wait for extruder temp
G28 ; move X/Y/Z to min endstops
G1 Z0.28 ; lift nozzle a bit
G92 E0
G1 Y3 F2400 ; zero the extruded length
G1 X180  E40 F500 ; Extrude 25mm of filament in a 5cm line.
G92 E0 ; zero the extruded length again
G1 E-2 F3000 ; Retract a little
G1 X181 F4000 ; Quickly wipe away from the filament line
M117

variants.name: Anycubic Kobra 3 0.2 nozzle
variants.startGcode:
G9111 bedTemp=[first_layer_bed_temperature] extruderTemp=[first_layer_temperature[initial_tool]]
M117
M900 K0.051
variants.endGcode:
G92 E0
G1 E-2 F3600
{if max_layer_z < max_print_height-1}G1 Z{max_layer_z+2} F900 ; Move print head further up{endif}
G1 X250 Y220 F12000 ; present print
M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M104 S0 ; turn off temperature
M107;turn off fan
M84; disable stepper motors
